wikipedia_page.main: Thomas Collinge (1898–1960) was an English footballer, the younger brother of Ernest Collinge.

response: Ernest Collinge (5 December 1895 – 15 December 1960) was an English footballer who played as a half-back for Port Vale in the 1920s. He was the elder brother of Tom Collinge.
* Ernest Collinge (1895–1960), English footballer and the elder brother of Tom Collinge
